<h1 style="text-align:center">How to use ValetBike </h1><hr/><br>
	<ol>
		<li>Access the Bikea webApp through your browser.</li>
		<li>Create a new profile if you're a new user, or log-in using "Profile" button on the navigation bar.</li>
		<li>If you wish to purchase a membership, choose a membership plan from the "Pricing and Plans" tab.</li>
		<li>Head to the closest ValetBike station to begin using your membership!</li>
		<li>To unlock a bike: go to "Unlock a Bike" tab to fill in bike information.</li>
			<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha; padding-bottom: 0;">
			<li style="margin-left:2em">This includes putting valid Bike ID which can be 
			found on the bike's handle and the station name.</li>
		 	</ol>
		<li>After use, please make sure to return the bike to a ValetBike station (that has an open dock).</li>
			<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha; padding-bottom: 0;">
			<li style="margin-left:2em">To complete return process, go to "Unlock a Bike" tab and return the bike. Please ensure to select the correct station name.</li>
			</ol>
		 </ol>


